Description_lang: $?a137013[Your Arcane abilities reduce the cooldown of Fury of Elune by ${$s1/-1000}.1 sec and the cooldown of New Moon, Half Moon, and Full Moon by ${$s2/-1000}.1 sec.][Your Arcane abilities reduce the cooldown of Lunar Beam by ${$s3/-1000}.1 sec.]
